    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>258516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_260_070_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>バンディ将軍、
あの子も養子候補ですか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>General Bundy, that child may be a suitable candidate for 
adoption. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>258712</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_260_070_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ……親も探してはみたが、
見つからなかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I realize... Despite the search no traces of her parents 
were found. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>258852</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_260_070_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>近頃、生活に困窮し
子どもを捨てる親が
増えています</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>More and more parents living in poverty kick away their 
kids. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>258852</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_260_070_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いくら呼びかけても
向こうは捨てたわけですから
名乗り出るわけありません</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even if they recognize the child, the opposite party may 
decide to ignore the notice of a missing child to free themselves 
of trouble. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>258992</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_260_070_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これもすべて……
長引く戦争で
民が飢えているせいか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is the result of a starving nation in the midst of an 
overtly long war... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
